rows.label: qst650101_msg0003
rows.name:
They musta come here from the
World Tree.

rows.label: qst650101_msg0005
rows.name:
I see no reason to leave them alive.
I'll erase them.

rows.label: qst650101_msg0006
rows.name:
Wait a sec! Let's watch them for a
bit first, yeah?

rows.label: qst650101_msg0008
rows.name:
The Driver of the Holy Grail and the
Flamebringer?!

rows.label: qst650101_msg0009
rows.name:
Your pursuit of us is formidable
in its relentlessness.

rows.label: qst650101_msg0010
rows.name:
Um, we weren't actually pursuing
anyone. This is a total coincidence.

rows.label: qst650101_msg0012
rows.name:
Or maybe this is a Praetor-given
opportunity?

rows.label: qst650101_msg0013
rows.name: Let's rid ourselves of these brats.

rows.label: qst650101_msg0015
rows.name:
Heh.
I could have saved us some time.

rows.label: qst650101_msg0017
rows.name:
Attention, maggots.
Your pitiful lives end here.
